{
  "id": "adv_main_03_05_04",
  "title": "BIG4編1章24話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "garden-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyodorm-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん。私、決めたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan. I’ve made up my mind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "うん、聞かせて？\nどんな答えでも……受け止めるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ tell me.\nWhatever your answer is… I’ll accept it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.3833560943,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "私、いっぱい考えたよ\n琴乃ちゃんについて行くか、残るか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought about it a lot.\nWhether to go with you or stay.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "それで……気付いたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And… I realized something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.3630388259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "私が大事にしたいのは、今はもう――\n琴乃ちゃんだけじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What I want to cherish now――\nis no longer just you‚ Kotono-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "私は、私達は、四人で頑張って……\n琴乃ちゃんがいつでも戻れるようにしておくから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I‚ we‚ will work hard as four…\nso that you can always come back‚ Kotono-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "だから私――琴乃ちゃんとは一緒に行けない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ I――I can’t go with you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.2681413171,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "……っ\n……そっか、分かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…!\n…I see‚ I understand.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.0459002272,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 51.1723138965
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "渚……沢山悩ませちゃってごめんね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa… I’m so sorry for making you worry so much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.1723138965,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "もう、ほんとだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ come on.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.7723138965,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "第一、私が琴乃ちゃんについて行ったら\n月ストが三人になっちゃうんだよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I went with you‚\nMoon Tempest would be down to three members‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.1766383906,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "う……ごめん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… I’m sorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.8413616653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "そのことは、なんていうか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That… I mean…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.2413616653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "渚のことで頭がいっぱいになってて……\n反省してるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was so preoccupied with you‚ Nagisa‚ that…\nI’m reflecting on it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.408028332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "う、うん。それならいいんだよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "O-Okay. That’s fine!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.1413616653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "四人で凄くなり過ぎて、琴乃ちゃんに「すぐにでも\n戻りたい～！」って思わせちゃったらごめんね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just promise me you’ll want to come back\nas soon as possible if we become too amazing as a four!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.1953607686,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "……言ってくれるじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You’re something else.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.3851034954,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "私も、また一緒にステージに立ちたいって\nみんなに思ってもらえるアイドルになって戻って来る",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll come back as an idol that everyone‚ including you‚\nwill want to see perform on stage again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.3517727053,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても……渚、変わったね\nちょっとびっくりした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You know… you’ve changed‚ Nagisa.\nI’m a little surprised.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.8184332683,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "うん。琴乃ちゃんのおかげで\n今までい～っぱい悩んできたからね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Thanks to you‚ Kotono-chan‚\nI’ve been through a lot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.9430279918,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "もう……ごめんってば",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on… I said I’m sorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.1479347382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "それに、私が変わったって言ったけど……\n琴乃ちゃんもだよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And‚ I said I’ve changed‚ but…\nyou have too‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.596227482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_achieve-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 117.5581814282
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "え？　そう……なの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? I… have?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.5581814282,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "前よりも、雰囲気がすっごく柔らかくなったよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’ve become a lot softer than before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.4248480949,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "それは……そうかも、しれないけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That… might be true.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.3646895242,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "なんていうか、ツンツンしなくなったよね！\nやっぱりアイドル活動の影響なのかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're not as prickly as you used to be!\nI wonder if it’s the influence of being an idol?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.3999969482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "それは……あると思う\nだって、いろんな人と出会ってきたでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think… that’s part of it.\nWe’ve met all sorts of people‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.5240119278,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロだけでも、年上の人だと\n{user}さんに、三枝さん、さとみさん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just in Hoshimi Prods alone‚\nthere’s {user}-san‚ Saegusa-san‚ Satomi-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.7333302815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんや莉央さんもお姉さん、って感じだしね\nそれに、沙季もすっごく落ち着いてる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san and Rio-san feel like older sisters too.\nAnd then there's Saki‚ who's super calm.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.0190888237,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "かと思えば、芽衣やすずみたいに、目を離した隙に\n何をするか分からない子もいるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And then there are Mei and Suzu‚ who could do\nanything when you take your eyes off them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.1857605766,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04-ngs016.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、そうだね\nすずちゃんはお金の使い方が凄かったっけ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha‚ you’re right.\nSuzu-chan’s spending habits are something else…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.4666636149,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04-ktn016.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣はもう、そのまま猫って感じ\nあちこちに興味を持ってすぐどこかに行っちゃうし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei is just like a cat.\nShe’s curious about everything and wanders off all the time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.7195703974,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04-ngs017.m4a",
      "text": "でも、月ストを結成して、お互いのことが\n分かるようになってからは、とっても楽しかったよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But after we formed Moon Tempest and\ngot to know each other‚ it was really fun‚ wasn’t it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.9666636149,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_moon-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 187.9450580428
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04-ktn017.m4a",
      "text": "バラバラでも、ううん、バラバラだからこそ……\n一つにまとまって成長出来るのが楽しかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though we were all different‚ no‚ because we were all different…\nit was fun to come together as one and grow.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.9450580428,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04-ngs018.m4a",
      "text": "デビューライブを頑張って、NEXT VENUS\nグランプリを勝ち抜いて、東京にやって来て……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We worked hard for our debut live‚ we won the NEXT VENUS\nGrand Prix‚ we came to Tokyo…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 194.0666636149,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_04-ktn018.m4a",
      "text": "本当に目まぐるしかったね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s been a whirlwind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 197.7096611172,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
